 Router Link 

 Router link is when we applied to and element in a template ,it makes that element a link that initiates navigation to a route.
 
 In simple words whenever we wnat to create a link in template then we use router link.
 
 Eg :--
      <a [routerLink]="['/user/zahid']"> Click To Redirect</a>
      
 This is not the only way we can also use buttons.
 
  We can have any number of router links in the template 

 Router Links can be static or can be dynamic in nature 

 Static Router Link -> <a [RouterLink]="'/user'"> </a>
 
 
 
